text: Kumanovo (; ) is a city in North Macedonia, near the capital city of Skopje. In 2002, 70,842 people lived there. This City is named after the Kumans.https://svilenkonac.net/2018/12/03/%D0%BA%D1%83%D0%BC%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%BE- kumanovo/ ==References== Category:Cities in North Macedonia
